

=Description=

"[[Social Peripheral Vision]], which is enabled by for example [[Lifelogging]] software, creates "the ability to have your finger on the pulse of your friends, family, and colleagues. Once you know what the people you care about are up to, you notice opportunities for social interaction that you would probably otherwise miss. Even just the simple knowledge that your loved ones are ok can have a lot of emotional value in an increasingly unstable world."
